href="https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-photo-mode-instagram-194215693.html">类似 TikTok 的功能</a>，该公司通过扩大社交功能来回报大家的青睐似乎是合乎逻辑的。然而，它强调，在尝试新事物时，视频仍然是其身份的核心。 TikTok 发言人告诉<em>Axios</em> ：“娱乐频道一直是 TikTok 商业模式的核心，即使我们正在尝试新功能来增强用户体验。”</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-job-postings-point-to-social-features-to-help-it-compete-with-meta-194332559.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-job-postings-point-to-social-features-to-help-it-compete-with-meta-194332559.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4c03a956-17ba-4a77-85ce-7b387c177040</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 19:43:32 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693943014</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T19:43:38+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="5760" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/4a3bedd0-4c20-11ee-be69-143fa016e6c6" width="8640"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="5760" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/4a3bedd0-4c20-11ee-be69-143fa016e6c6" width="8640"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - The icon for the video sharing TikTok app is seen on a smartphone, F